      minute interval, then a single aviciSonetFarEndPathEvent notification
      will be generated."
   DEFVAL { 1 }
   ::= { aviciSonetFarEndPathEntry 3 }

aviciSonetFarEndPathThresholdUAS OBJECT-TYPE
   SYNTAX         Unsigned32 (1..900)
   MAX-ACCESS     read-create
   STATUS         current
   DESCRIPTION    
      "This variable specifies a threshold for the number of Far End
      Unavailable Seconds encountered by a SONET/SDH path entity in the
      current fifteen minute interval.  If the value of
      sonetFarEndPathCurrentUASs becomes greater than or equal to this
      value in the current fifteen minute interval, then a single
