   DEFVAL { 1 }
   ::= { aviciSonetFarEndPathEntry 4 }

aviciSonetFarEndPathEventEnable OBJECT-TYPE
   SYNTAX         Integer32 (0..32)
   MAX-ACCESS     read-create
   STATUS         current
   DESCRIPTION    
      "This variable specifies the type of events that will be generated for
      this corresponding SONET/SDH far-end path entity.  The value represents a
      vector of bits, each controlling a unique event:

         - Bit 0   Rising threshold alarm, sonetSectionCurrentESs.
